name: 38/∞ • in meditative breathing rhythm
description: experiment nº 38 from my series "•/∞" (2020), where I created images made with mobile apps. this one was made with mirrorlab's deform tool and animated with movee video app. original photography taken by vini cassol and edited on lightroom: 2019, fundación proa, la boca, buenos aires - argentina, in front of dan flavin "Untitled (to Donna) 6, 1971" artpiece.
